just like you two.

17:47.867 --> 17:49.436
Yeah, fine. Maybe you will.

17:49.469 --> 17:51.371
Maybe you will be just like me.

17:51.404 --> 17:52.805
Maybe there'll
be an accident,

17:52.839 --> 17:55.175
